BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:IsTdlIU6wzKiR1ymuvQRK
SUMMARY:Color festival – Redmond
DTSTAMP:20260306T013340Z
DTSTART:20260308T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Redmond (15 miles NE)\n\nAttended by 10\,000 people\, Festival 
	of Color has music\, dancers\, food vendors\, and colored powder flying th
	rough the air at Redmond City Hall Campus\, 15670 NE 85th St. in Redmond. 
	Admission and parking are free\, but there is a cost to buy colored powder
	.\n\nhttps://www.festivalofcolor.us/\n\nFrom Events12 Seattle
